replies.body:
PvP.net connection errors most often occur when there are drops in your connection to the service ( like packet loss, as you mentioned). A good place to start in finding a fix is to ensure your local settings are good with our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if you still see this issue after those steps.
